    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ONE STORY THROUGH MULTIPLE EPISODES - LIKE A TV SHOW!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story that unfolds across multiple episodes, each with new mysteries and thrilling twists and explanations of what's happening. You play as the same character in all episodes, but sometimes you may play as side characters in the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start your journey in Episode 1 by exploring atmospheric locations and piecing together the start of the narrative of Forest Ranger Services.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283900/extras/7716004223ba784a43527a4b64f7221c.poster.avif?t=1762941933\" width=600 height=253 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283900/extras/7716004223ba784a43527a4b64f7221c.webm?t=1762941933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXAMINE YOUR SURROUNDINGS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the levels and find details, lore and clues - Try to figure out the plot of the series.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283900/extras/245da746926ea4b8dd4ffeb4eb7025b3.poster.avif?t=1762941933\" width=600 height=253 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283900/extras/245da746926ea4b8dd4ffeb4eb7025b3.webm?t=1762941933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DRIVE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go for a ride in a forest and listen to a radio station podcast about missing hikers and UFOs all based on facts, documented reports and real life events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283900/extras/9d71d25e513507bcf6b579d74967c12c.poster.avif?t=1762941933\" width=600 height=253 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283900/extras/9d71d25e513507bcf6b579d74967c12c.webm?t=1762941933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>YOU ARE THE MAIN CHARACTER OF THE SERIES!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the events that start the Forest Ranger Services series where you are the main character. Find all the clues in the first episode.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Piece together the creepy start of the series - a non-linear story!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk to strange individuals - meet some of the main characters and follow their story through the episodes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casual driving with a twist!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Forest Ranger Services series are based on real life events and personal accounts of hikers. The narrative has been altered for entertainment purposes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are thousands of missing reports filed each year in the U.S National Parks. Many cases remain unexplained. </p>",
